      "created": "2017-04-25T23:30:03.532+0000",
      "description": "The example provided with SLS appears to be broken - I didn't see any jobs running.  On top of that, it seems like getting SLS to run properly requires a lot of hadoop site configs, scheduler configs, etc.  I was only able to get something running after [~yufeigu] provided a lot of config files.\n\nWe should provide a better out-of-the-box experience for SLS.  ",
